  README.md,project,document duplicate-skip semantics for test-all
body: "Problem: when multiple items link the same test command/path, pm test-all executes duplicates repeatedly. Proposed behavior: skip duplicate command/path entries within a single test-all run while preserving deterministic results and reporting."
